OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773245484
OL,3,CVisitors urged to keep safe distance
OL,4,Cfrom highland cattle after viral TikTok
OL,6,FKent Wildlife Trust is urging people
OL,7,Fto keep a safe distance from its
OL,8,Fhighland cattle after it saw a surge
OL,9,Fin visitor numbers linked to viral
OL,10,Fsocial media content.
OL,12,FA recent TikTok video featuring
OL,13,Fhighland cows at Hothfield Heathlands
OL,14,Fled to a notable increase in people
OL,15,Factively approaching and attempting to
OL,16,Fstroke the animals.
OL,18,FThe Trust says this poses a risk to
OL,19,Fvisitors and to the cattle.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
