OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773245484
OL,3,CVisitors urged to keep safe distance
OL,4,Cfrom highland cattle after viral TikTok
OL,6,FJessica Allam, Senior Wilder Grazing
OL,7,FRanger at Kent Wildlife Trust, said:
OL,8,F"We love that our highland cows have
OL,9,Fcaptured people's hearts online and
OL,10,Fseeing so many people coming out to
OL,11,Fenjoy Hothfield Heathlands, but we're
OL,12,Fasking people to remember that these
OL,13,Fare not pets - they are conservation
OL,14,Fgrazers doing an important job.
OL,16,F"Getting too close causes them real
OL,17,Fdistress and can put both the visitor
OL,18,Fand the animal at risk. Please don't
OL,19,Ftouch them and give them the space
OL,20,Fthey need."
