OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773245484
OL,3,CVisitors urged to keep safe distance
OL,4,Cfrom highland cattle after viral TikTok
OL,6,FVisitors to Hothfield Heathlands and
OL,7,Fany reserve with grazing animals are
OL,8,Fbeing urged to always keep a minimum
OL,9,Fdistance of 10 metres from all
OL,10,Flivestock and to not attempt to touch,
OL,11,Ffeed, or approach the animals.
OL,13,FDogs should also be kept on a short
OL,14,Flead and under control.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
